450
00:21:56.773 --> 00:22:00.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When the Third Dynasty
was founded ten years later,

451
00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:02.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
