were given the titles

452
00:22:02.696 --> 00:22:06.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the names of the original
Imperial Family...

453
00:22:06.700 --> 00:22:09.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to create the <i>illusion</i>
of an unbroken line.

454
00:22:09.578 --> 00:22:12.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, the woman
that you think of

455
00:22:12.247 --> 00:22:14.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
