462
00:22:34.102 --> 00:22:36.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But who cares about facts?

463
00:22:36.104 --> 00:22:39.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The chronicle says that you have
Imperial blood in your veins,

464
00:22:39.649 --> 00:22:42.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and that's exactly what
we'll keep telling everyone.

465
00:22:45.947 --> 00:22:49.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Continue with the saga.

466
00:22:49.284 --> 00:22:51.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My pleasure.

467
00:22:53.663 --> 00:22:55.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
