00:25:55.929 --> 00:25:57.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm going to kill Worf.

527
00:25:59.432 --> 00:26:01.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm going to kill Worf.

