604
00:29:40.069 --> 00:29:41.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Excuse me, sir.

605
00:29:50.955 --> 00:29:51.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jadzia

606
00:29:51.956 --> 00:29:53.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
we need to...

607
00:29:57.212 --> 00:29:58.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're mad.

608
00:29:58.797 --> 00:30:01.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am concerned.

609
00:30:01.633 --> 00:30:03.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, well, I'm hung over.

610
00:30:03.718 --> 00:30:05.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Can we talk later?

611
00:30:05.303 --> 00:30:07.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We have a very
serious problem.

612
00:30:07.847 --> 00:30:10.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sirella has canceled
the wedding.

613
00:30:10.475 --> 00:30:13.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She doesn't waste
any time, does she?

614
00:30:13.353 --> 00:30:15.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She said
you attacked her.

615
00:30:16.773 --> 00:30:18.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She pulled a knife.

616
00:30:23.321 --> 00:30:26.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You are forbidden to join
the House of Martok.

617
00:30:26.115 --> 00:30:28.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So I won't be invited
to the family picnics.

618
00:30:28.827 --> 00:30:30.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll live.

619
00:30:30.829 --> 00:30:33.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I cannot believe
how you're taking this so lightly.

620
00:30:33.581 --> 00:30:34.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you hear that?

621
00:30:34.833 --> 00:30:36.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

622
00:30:36.334 --> 00:30:37.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>muffled voices </i>)

623
00:30:37.794 --> 00:30:39.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It sounds like voices.

624
00:30:45.468 --> 00:30:46.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hi.
-Hi.

625
00:30:46.928 --> 00:30:49.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ODO:
Is the party over?

626
00:30:49.097 --> 00:30:52.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You could say that.
It's 10:30.

627
00:30:52.642 --> 00:30:55.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
In the morning?
I'm on duty.

628
00:30:55.228 --> 00:30:56.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So am I.

629
00:30:56.855 --> 00:30:57.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It was a great party.

630
00:30:58.022 --> 00:30:59.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thanks.

631
00:31:06.364 --> 00:31:08.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We must deal
with the situation now.

632
00:31:08.408 --> 00:31:11.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Stop yelling.
My head hurts.

633
00:31:11.953 --> 00:31:15.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You must go to Sirella
and beg her forgiveness.

634
00:31:22.255 --> 00:31:24.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don't beg.

635
00:31:24.173 --> 00:31:27.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You are allowing
your pride to blind you.

636
00:31:27.886 --> 00:31:29.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Look who's talking.

637
00:31:29.429 --> 00:31:31.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You want me to go crawling
to some old hag

638
00:31:31.306 --> 00:31:33.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
just so you can have your
traditional Klingon wedding.

639
00:31:33.474 --> 00:31:36.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is about more
than just tradition.

640
00:31:38.438 --> 00:31:41.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You and I have embarked
on a spiritual journey,

641
00:31:41.900 --> 00:31:43.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
one that will
bind us together

642
00:31:43.443 --> 00:31:45.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
through this life
and into the next.

643
00:31:45.612 --> 00:31:47.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You cannot turn back now.

644
00:31:47.363 --> 00:31:49.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Maybe you're on
a spiritual journey, Worf,

645
00:31:49.991 --> 00:31:51.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but I just want
to get married.

646
00:31:52.035 --> 00:31:55.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So why don't you go back
to sweating and bleeding

647
00:31:55.747 --> 00:31:57.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
with your friends
in the holosuite,

648
00:31:57.582 --> 00:31:58.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and when you're done,

649
00:31:59.042 --> 00:32:00.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
meet me in
Benjamin's office

650
00:32:00.835 --> 00:32:02.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and he'll perform
the ceremony.

651
00:32:10.762 --> 00:32:12.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If that is your attitude...

652
00:32:15.266 --> 00:32:17.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
perhaps Sirella
was right about you.

653
00:32:20.647 --> 00:32:23.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There should be no wedding.

654
00:32:24.275 --> 00:32:26.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's fine with me.

655
00:32:29.030 --> 00:32:31.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door opens, closes </i>)

656
00:32:45.755 --> 00:32:49.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>whistling </i>)

657
00:32:49.926 --> 00:32:51.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What's going on?

658
00:32:51.344 --> 00:32:52.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Haven't you heard?

659
00:32:52.428 --> 00:32:53.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The wedding's off.

660
00:32:53.554 --> 00:32:55.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Off? Why?

661
00:32:55.348 --> 00:33:00.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She says it's because
he's a pig-headed, stubborn man

662
00:33:00.228 --> 00:33:02.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who puts tradition
before everything else.

663
00:33:02.772 --> 00:33:05.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He says it's because
she's a frivolous

664
00:33:05.274 --> 00:33:06.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
emotional woman

665
00:33:06.859 --> 00:33:09.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who refuses to take him
or his culture seriously.

666
00:33:09.320 --> 00:33:11.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You can see
the problem.

667
00:33:11.614 --> 00:33:13.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They're both right.

668
00:33:13.241 --> 00:33:14.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Exactly.

669
00:33:14.575 --> 00:33:17.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well... there's only
one thing for it.

670
00:33:19.080 --> 00:33:21.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dinner.

671
00:33:21.290 --> 00:33:23.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll get the menu.

672
00:33:31.551 --> 00:33:33.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door chimes </i>)

673
00:33:33.136 --> 00:33:34.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Enter.

674
00:33:41.602 --> 00:33:43.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Worf...

675
00:33:43.855 --> 00:33:45.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
you've made a grave error.

676
00:33:48.151 --> 00:33:50.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Perhaps.

677
00:33:51.029 --> 00:33:53.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you still love her?

678
00:33:53.364 --> 00:33:55.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course.

679
00:33:55.491 --> 00:33:58.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
However, in this
case, <i>that...</i>

680
00:33:58.578 --> 00:34:00.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
may not be enough.

681
00:34:02.707 --> 00:34:05.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Anyone can see that we are
hopelessly mismatched.

682
00:34:05.793 --> 00:34:07.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is a Trill;
I am a Klingon.

683
00:34:08.046 --> 00:34:10.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She has had
five marriages.

684
00:34:10.798 --> 00:34:13.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This would be my first.

685
00:34:13.092 --> 00:34:16.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When she is laughing,
I am somber.

686
00:34:16.095 --> 00:34:17.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When I am happy,
she is crying.

687
00:34:18.056 --> 00:34:21.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She plays <i>tongo </i>with
the Ferengi bartender.

688
00:34:21.225 --> 00:34:23.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can barely stand him.

689
00:34:25.688 --> 00:34:28.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She mocks everything...

690
00:34:28.649 --> 00:34:31.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
while I take
everything seriously.

691
00:34:33.946 --> 00:34:36.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is nothing like the woman
I thought I would marry.

692
00:34:38.951 --> 00:34:41.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We are not accorded
the luxury

693
00:34:41.370 --> 00:34:44.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
of choosing the women
we fall in love with.

694
00:34:44.916 --> 00:34:47.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you think Sirella
is anything like the woman

695
00:34:47.835 --> 00:34:49.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I thought that I'd marry?

696
00:34:51.464 --> 00:34:56.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She is a prideful,
arrogant, mercurial woman

697
00:34:56.552 --> 00:35:01.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who shares my bed far too
infrequently for my taste.

698
00:35:02.475 --> 00:35:04.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And yet...

699
00:35:06.104 --> 00:35:08.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I love her...

700
00:35:08.481 --> 00:35:10.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
deeply.

701
00:35:10.566 --> 00:35:12.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm.

702
00:35:12.527 --> 00:35:16.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We Klingons often tout our...

703
00:35:16.989 --> 00:35:19.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
prowess in battle...

704
00:35:19.158 --> 00:35:24.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
our desire for glory and honor
above all else...

705
00:35:24.497 --> 00:35:27.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but how hollow is
the sound of victory...

706
00:35:27.959 --> 00:35:30.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
without someone
to share it with?

707
00:35:31.045 --> 00:35:34.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Honor gives
little comfort

708
00:35:34.257 --> 00:35:36.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to a man alone
in his home...

709
00:35:36.384 --> 00:35:39.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and in his heart.

710
00:35:44.809 --> 00:35:46.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
One steak with mushrooms

711
00:35:46.561 --> 00:35:48.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
baked potato, sour cream
and chives.

712
00:35:48.312 --> 00:35:49.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I should have had that.

713
00:35:49.856 --> 00:35:53.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
One double Altair sandwich,
no mustard...

714
00:35:53.192 --> 00:35:54.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
two bowls of linguini,

715
00:35:55.069 --> 00:35:58.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bajoran shrimp
with extra cheese.

716
00:35:58.114 --> 00:36:00.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
One loaf of mapa bread.

717
00:36:00.741 --> 00:36:02.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Quark, where's
the <i>kava </i>juice?

718
00:36:02.618 --> 00:36:03.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They're still
squeezing the roots

719
00:36:03.828 --> 00:36:05.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
unless you want replicated.

720
00:36:05.371 --> 00:36:06.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We'll wait.

721
00:36:06.789 --> 00:36:08.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
SISKO:
What do you think you're doing?

722
00:36:09.750 --> 00:36:10.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The wedding's
been called off.

723
00:36:10.918 --> 00:36:12.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's back on.

724
00:36:12.128 --> 00:36:14.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf is apologizing
to Jadzia

725
00:36:14.755 --> 00:36:16.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
at this very moment.

726
00:36:16.090 --> 00:36:17.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Quark, take
it all away.

727
00:36:17.717 --> 00:36:20.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No food for those
on the path to <i>Kal'Hyah.</i>

728
00:36:20.553 --> 00:36:23.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No refunds for those on the path
to <i>Kal'Hyah </i>as well.

729
00:36:23.598 --> 00:36:24.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorry.

730
00:36:29.729 --> 00:36:31.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Father, what happened?

731
00:36:34.442 --> 00:36:36.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She refused
to change her mind

732
00:36:36.402 --> 00:36:38.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and the wedding is still off.

733
00:36:38.571 --> 00:36:39.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>sighs </i>)

734
00:36:39.822 --> 00:36:40.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where is she?

735
00:36:40.948 --> 00:36:42.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
In her quarters.

736
00:36:42.992 --> 00:36:45.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll go talk to her.

737
00:36:45.203 --> 00:36:48.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Just... keep them away
from the food?

738
00:36:55.588 --> 00:36:56.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>door chimes </i>)

739
00:36:56.714 --> 00:36:57.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Come in!

740
00:36:59.842 --> 00:37:01.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Save your breath.

741
00:37:01.135 --> 00:37:03.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf's gone too far,
and now it's over.

742
00:37:03.512 --> 00:37:05.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you know what
he wanted me to do?

743
00:37:05.640 --> 00:37:08.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He wanted me to go crawling
on my hands and knees to Sirella

744
00:37:08.935 --> 00:37:10.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
to beg her forgiveness.

745
00:37:10.519 --> 00:37:11.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beg her! Me!

746
00:37:11.979 --> 00:37:13.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I was once

747
00:37:13.731 --> 00:37:16.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the Federation Ambassador
to the Klingon Empire.

748
00:37:19.028 --> 00:37:20.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I negotiated
the Khitomer Accords

749
00:37:21.030 --> 00:37:22.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
before Worf
was even born.

750
00:37:22.531 --> 00:37:24.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Curzon negotiated the Accords!

751
00:37:24.659 --> 00:37:26.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I've got news for you,
old man.

752
00:37:26.160 --> 00:37:27.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're not Curzon anymore.

753
00:37:27.912 --> 00:37:30.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And what the hell is that
supposed to mean?

754
00:37:30.248 --> 00:37:32.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It means that you
can't expect Sirella

755
00:37:32.166 --> 00:37:33.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
to treat you like Curzon

756
00:37:33.459 --> 00:37:35.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
just because you carry
his memories.

757
00:37:35.836 --> 00:37:37.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
To her, you're just
a young woman

758
00:37:37.338 --> 00:37:39.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
who decided to marry
into her family.

759
00:37:39.632 --> 00:37:41.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If it means
you have to bow down

760
00:37:41.175 --> 00:37:42.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and kiss her boots,

761
00:37:42.843 --> 00:37:46.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that's exactly what you have
to do, and you knew that.

762
00:37:46.138 --> 00:37:48.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The moment you decided
to marry Worf,

763
00:37:48.516 --> 00:37:50.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you knew that sooner or later
you'd have to bow down

764
00:37:50.810 --> 00:37:53.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and show her the respect
that she's due.

765
00:37:53.521 --> 00:37:55.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is Worf's fault--

766
00:37:55.189 --> 00:37:57.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf and his traditional
Klingon wedding.

767
00:37:57.900 --> 00:38:00.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, he may have let
this wedding business

768
00:38:00.194 --> 00:38:04.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
go to his head,
but you are 356 years old.

769
00:38:04.365 --> 00:38:07.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Compared to you,
Worf is just a kid.

770
00:38:07.326 --> 00:38:10.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And if you can't abide
by Klingon traditions,

771
00:38:10.454 --> 00:38:11.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
then you never should
have let yourself

772
00:38:11.998 --> 00:38:14.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
fall in love with him
in the first place.

773
00:38:16.544 --> 00:38:19.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And you <i>are</i>
in love with him.

774
00:38:22.300 --> 00:38:24.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wasn't looking
to fall in love.

775
00:38:24.302 --> 00:38:27.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I was perfectly happy
by myself.

776
00:38:27.513 --> 00:38:30.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I had friends, a career,
adventure...

777
00:38:33.602 --> 00:38:36.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then one day...

778
00:38:36.939 --> 00:38:39.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
this Klingon
with a bad attitude

779
00:38:39.734 --> 00:38:41.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
walked into my life

780
00:38:41.319 --> 00:38:45.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the next thing I know,
I'm getting married.

781
00:38:45.656 --> 00:38:49.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
After 356 years
and seven lifetimes...

782
00:38:51.287 --> 00:38:53.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I still lead with my heart.

783
00:38:53.914 --> 00:38:57.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know, that is
what I've always loved about you.

784
00:39:00.296 --> 00:39:03.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I think that's why
Worf loves you, too.

785
00:39:09.055 --> 00:39:12.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>sighs </i>)

786
00:39:12.141 --> 00:39:18.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Whatever happened to that
young, callow Ensign I used to know?

787
00:39:18.773 --> 00:39:21.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The one who used
to turn to me

788
00:39:21.317 --> 00:39:23.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
for advice all the time?

789
00:39:23.527 --> 00:39:27.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know,
the one with hair?

790
00:39:27.490 --> 00:39:29.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I grew up.

791
00:39:33.662 --> 00:39:36.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I guess it's time
I grow up, too.

792
00:39:36.749 --> 00:39:38.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mmm.

793
00:40:19.417 --> 00:40:21.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
With fire and steel

794
00:40:21.752 --> 00:40:25.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
did the gods forge
the Klingon heart.

795
00:40:25.339 --> 00:40:27.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So fiercely did it beat,

796
00:40:27.174 --> 00:40:31.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so loud was the sound,
that the gods cried out,

797
00:40:31.137 --> 00:40:34.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"On this day
we have brought forth

798
00:40:34.223 --> 00:40:37.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"the strongest heart
in all the heavens.

799
00:40:37.852 --> 00:40:41.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"None can stand before it
without trembling

800
00:40:41.313 --> 00:40:42.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
at its strength."

801
00:40:42.815 --> 00:40:46.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But then the Klingon heart
weakened

802
00:40:46.318 --> 00:40:48.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
its steady rhythm faltered
and the gods said,

803
00:40:48.988 --> 00:40:51.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Why have you weakened so?

804
00:40:51.240 --> 00:40:52.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"We have made you the strongest

805
00:40:52.783 --> 00:40:55.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
in all of creation."

806
00:40:55.828 --> 00:40:57.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And the heart said...

807
00:40:57.705 --> 00:40:58.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am alone.

808
00:41:00.958 --> 00:41:03.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And the gods knew
that they had erred.

809
00:41:03.210 --> 00:41:05.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So they went back
to their forge

810
00:41:05.129 --> 00:41:08.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and brought forth...
another heart.

811
00:41:37.453 --> 00:41:41.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But the second heart
beat stronger than the first,

812
00:41:41.916 --> 00:41:44.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the first was jealous
of its power.

813
00:41:49.006 --> 00:41:50.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fortunately...

814
00:41:50.841 --> 00:41:52.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the second heart
was tempered

815
00:41:52.343 --> 00:41:53.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
by wisdom.

816
00:41:53.928 --> 00:41:57.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If we join together,
no force can stop us.

817
00:42:05.147 --> 00:42:08.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And when the two hearts
began to beat together,

818
00:42:08.567 --> 00:42:12.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
they filled the heavens
with a terrible sound.

819
00:42:12.571 --> 00:42:16.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
For the first time,
the gods knew fear.

820
00:42:16.534 --> 00:42:19.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They tried to flee,
but it was too late.

821
00:42:19.537 --> 00:42:22.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The Klingon hearts
destroyed the gods

822
00:42:22.790 --> 00:42:23.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
who created them

823
00:42:24.083 --> 00:42:27.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and turned the heavens
to ashes.

824
00:42:27.378 --> 00:42:29.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
To this very day

825
00:42:29.213 --> 00:42:34.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
no one can oppose the beating
of two Klingon hearts.

826
00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:38.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not even me.

827
00:42:42.476 --> 00:42:46.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Worf, son of Mogh,
does your heart beat

828
00:42:46.647 --> 00:42:48.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
only for this woman?

829
00:42:48.899 --> 00:42:50.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

830
00:42:51.026 --> 00:42:54.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And will you swear
to join with her

831
00:42:54.154 --> 00:42:57.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and stand with her
against all who oppose you?

832
00:42:57.366 --> 00:42:59.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I swear.

833
00:42:59.994 --> 00:43:02.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jadzia, daughter of Kela,

834
00:43:02.746 --> 00:43:06.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
does your heart beat
only for this man?

835
00:43:06.584 --> 00:43:08.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

836
00:43:08.669 --> 00:43:10.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And do you swear
to join with him

837
00:43:10.921 --> 00:43:12.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and stand with him

838
00:43:12.298 --> 00:43:13.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
against all
who would oppose you?

839
00:43:15.426 --> 00:43:16.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
( <i>whispering </i>):
I swear.

840
00:43:18.304 --> 00:43:20.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then let all present
here today know

841
00:43:20.889 --> 00:43:25.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that this man
and this woman are married.

842
00:43:25.686 --> 00:43:27.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>applause </i>)

843
00:43:33.360 --> 00:43:34.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now?

844
00:43:34.903 --> 00:43:36.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not yet.

845
00:43:43.996 --> 00:43:44.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now?

846
00:43:44.997 --> 00:43:46.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Patience.

847
00:43:49.084 --> 00:43:50.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My Lady.

848
00:43:52.212 --> 00:43:54.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Welcome to the House
of Martok...

849
00:43:55.966 --> 00:43:57.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
my daughter.

850
00:44:02.181 --> 00:44:03.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now, Doctor!

851
00:44:03.807 --> 00:44:06.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
( <i>yelling </i>)

